OL,6,FFrench minister says P&O crews work
OL,7,F'dangerous' hours and is 'really
OL,8,Fshocked' by ITV News and the Guardian
OL,9,Fthat the firm .
OL,11,FUntil now, the law has allowed P&O to
OL,12,F, on both sides of the Channel.
OL,14,FToday - in France - the law changed.
OL,16,FIn Paris, the French Maritime
OL,17,FMinister, Herve Berville, signed a
OL,18,Fdecree enacting the "Against Social-
OL,19,FDumping On The English Channel" law.
OL,20,FIt is a law that has been inspired by
OL,21,FP&O Ferries.
