OL,3,CFrance changes law on ferry crew wages
OL,4,Cafter conditions deemed 'dangerous'
OL,6,F"We were really shocked by what
OL,7,Fhappened in March 2022," Mr Berville
OL,8,Ftold ITV News.
OL,10,F"We couldn't accept that . So we
OL,11,Fneeded to do something.
OL,13,F"Not only react, but to show that
OL,14,Fpolitics, show that to protect
OL,15,Fcitizens and seafarers."
OL,17,FThe new law forces all cross-Channel
OL,18,Fferry operators to pay at least the
OL,19,FFrench minimum wage of #9.96 an hour
OL,20,Fand limits the hours the agency crew
OL,21,Fare able to work without rest.
