OL,6,FITV News and the Guardian have seen
OL,7,Frecent payslips which show .
OL,9,FP&O also currently expects some crew
OL,10,Fto work seven days a week, for up to
OL,11,F17 weeks at a time, without a break.
OL,13,FHerve Berville describe this practice
OL,14,Fas "dangerous" and "not moral".
OL,16,FThe new law stipulates crews working
OL,17,Fon ships which dock at French ports
OL,18,Fcan work a maximum of 14 consecutive
OL,19,Fdays on shift, followed by 14 days off.
