OL,6,F"Can you imagine working for two
OL,7,Fmonths without a single day of rest?"
OL,8,FMr Berville said. "How can you, after
OL,9,Ftwo months, be in full command of what
OL,10,Fyou're doing?"
OL,12,FThe new law was passed unanimously by
OL,13,FAssemblee nationale and it gives ferry
OL,14,Foperators three months to comply. If
OL,15,Fthey don't, they will face sanctions.
