OL,6,FPersistent breaches will result in a
OL,7,Ffine for the ferry company of up to
OL,8,F7,500 Euros (#7,400) for each crew
OL,9,Fmember involved, and a fine and a
OL,10,Fpossible prison sentence of up to six
OL,11,Fmonths for executives.
OL,13,FP&O's competitors say that cutting its
OL,14,Fwage bill has enabled the company to
OL,15,Fcut its prices, giving it an unfair
OL,16,Fadvantage - on the busy Dover-Calais
OL,17,Froute, P&O is winning customers.
OL,19,FBrittany Ferries does pay the French
OL,20,Fminimum wage.
