OL,6,FThe company's president told me that
OL,7,Fwithout action by the French
OL,8,Fgovernment, his company would either
OL,9,Fdisappear or have to copy P&O.
OL,11,F"I'm not prepared to do that," Jean-
OL,12,FMarc Roue said.
OL,14,FP&O could choose to appeal against the
OL,15,Fnew law but the company hasn't said
OL,16,Fhow it intends to respond.
OL,18,FP&O has also insisted that its crew
OL,19,Fare properly rested.
